  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 85baba632ea3086499e53d211ed4c41a, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day1 - Intro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  lines:
  - speaker: 0
    text: "There\u2019s 15 days left until Valentine\u2019s Day but Alex suddenly
      decides that she wants to make this year\u2019s FEBIBIG extra special by giving
      her boyfriend the \u201Cperfect\u201D gift"
  - speaker: 1
    text: "Hmmm\u2026 I really want to get him the perfect gift this year. I wonder
      if I can do it with my P800 allowance? "
  - speaker: 2
    text: Allowance Received!
  - speaker: 1
    text: If I really want to make this work then I have to be smart with how I spend
      my money. I should probably look up some ways to better manage it theni. Maybe
      a budget system?
